metadata.name: Universe of Time #1/55
metadata.description:
"Universe of Time", UOT for short, was created by COUDE 2020 exclusively for the Flux Collective as a stencil artwork. It features the Flux Collective logo at the center of humanity's most important symbols. With the name of the artwork, COUDE also honored one of the greatest artists of the Fluxus movement, Ben Vautier. Ben claimed early on that "everything is time". Now COUDE brings the monumental work as a physical print edition by  
www.urbanshit-gallery.com.  
Each Print buyer will receive a UOT NFT for free
